  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueObject
  currentLines:
  - Hey, I'm Poly! Welcome to Employee Training!
  - I've got an task for you!
  - Drop off this package in that parking zone over there.
  - You will recieve money based on how fast you deliver it.
  - Don't let the time run out though. Or, the customer will get mad.
